graph TB
    subgraph "Model Registry Operator"
        Controller[Controller Manager<br/>Deployment]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Port 9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Controller -->|validates/mutates| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "ModelRegistry Instance (per CR)"
        REST[REST Server<br/>Port 8080/TCP HTTP]
        GRPC[gRPC Server<br/>Port 9090/TCP gRPC]
        Proxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Port 8443/TCP HTTPS]

        Proxy -->|forwards| REST
        REST -.->|sidecar| GRPC
    end

    subgraph "Database Backend"
        PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 16<br/>Port 5432/TCP]
        MySQL[MySQL 8.x<br/>Port 3306/TCP]
    end

    User[User/Client] -->|creates| ModelRegistryCR[ModelRegistry CR<br/>v1beta1]
    ModelRegistryCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates/manages| REST
    Controller -->|creates/manages| GRPC
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Proxy
    Controller -->|creates/manages| PostgreSQL

    REST -->|stores metadata| PostgreSQL
    REST -->|stores metadata| MySQL
    GRPC -->|stores metadata| PostgreSQL
    GRPC -->|stores metadata| MySQL

    Controller -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>Port 6443/TCP HTTPS]
    Controller -.->|optional| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA]
    Controller -.->|optional| Istio[Istio Service Mesh]

    ExternalClient[External Client] -->|HTTPS 443| Router[OpenShift Router]
    Router -->|HTTPS 8443| Proxy

    InternalClient[Internal Client] -->|HTTP 8080| REST
    InternalClient -->|gRPC 9090| GRPC

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style REST fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style GRPC fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Proxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelRegistryCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PostgreSQL fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MySQL fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceCA fill:#d3d3d3,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Istio fill:#d3d3d3,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
